        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-violet-400 pl-4 sm:pl-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-base mb-2">04. Vote to Prioritize</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            Everyone gets 3 votes to spend on the items that matter most. Cards and groups sort by vote count
