        </div>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-emerald-400 pl-4 sm:pl-6">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-base mb-2">05. Act: Create Sprint Actions</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
            Work through top-voted feedback together. Create action items with owners and due dates for your next sprint.
            Actions persist after the retro endsâ€”track progress and drive continuous improvement.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

